INSTALL GUIDE

1. Install Kali Linux VM

Download ISO:
Go to https://www.kali.org/get-kali/#kali-virtual-machines.

Install Virtualization Software: 
Download and install VirtualBox or VMware.

Create a New VM:
Allocate at least 2 GB RAM and 20 GB storage.

Load ISO and Install:
Boot from the downloaded ISO and follow the on-screen installation steps.

2. Install Debian Linux VM
Download ISO:
Go to https://www.debian.org/distrib/.

Install Virtualization Software:
Use VirtualBox or VMware.

Create a New VM:
Allocate at least 2 GB RAM and 20 GB storage.

Load ISO and Install:
Boot from the ISO and follow the guided installation.

3. Install Hydra Tool

On Kali or Debian:
sudo apt update
sudo apt install hydra

Verify Installation:
hydra -h

4. Install Hashcat Tool

On Kali or Debian:
sudo apt update
sudo apt install hashcat

Verify Installation:
hashcat --version

5. Install John the Ripper Tool

On Kali:
Pre-installed in Kali Linux.
john --version

On Debian:
sudo apt update
sudo apt install john

Verify Installation:
john --version

